  "detailed_description": "CBO TD is a build your own maze tower defense. Protect your city from hordes of mobs with different classes of towers and more efficient mazes. Mobs have Their own strengths and weaknesses, so picking the right tower and upgrades is imperative. Welcome back to days of old, where building the maze is half the fun.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2867380/extras/80a6f931d0761e0a96cd8371daac51a8.poster.avif?t=1725162192\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2867380/extras/80a6f931d0761e0a96cd8371daac51a8.webm?t=1725162192\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2867380/extras/80a6f931d0761e0a96cd8371daac51a8.mp4?t=1725162192\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Build your own maze<br>Multiple tower classes<br>Multiple monsters tiers<br>Unique monster strengths, Armor/Magic resist/Speed<br>Increasing wave size per round<br>Boss rounds every ten rounds<br>Stronger tiers of monsters added to the existing tiers every ten rounds<br>Random strength/weakness picked on start of new tiers<br>Single Player for the time being<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2867380/extras/911fb2f7331bac85fcd9d741dcde5e6b.poster.avif?t=1725162192\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2867380/extras/911fb2f7331bac85fcd9d741dcde5e6b.webm?t=1725162192\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2867380/extras/911fb2f7331bac85fcd9d741dcde5e6b.mp4?t=1725162192\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>New updates In progress<br>Co-op last man standing online game play, upgrades, more tower classes, balance changes, and updates are being built as you read this.",
